headline: Dollar Tree, Inc. to Host 2025 Investor Conference
summary: CHESAPEAKE, Va., September 16, 2025--Dollar Tree, Inc. (NASDAQ: DLTR) today announced that it will host an Investor Conference at the NASDAQ MarketSite in New York, NY on Wednesday, Oct. 15, 2025.

headline: Is Dollar Tree Stock Outperforming the Nasdaq?
summary: Although Dollar Tree has outpaced the broader Nasdaq Composite over the past year, Wall Street analysts remain cautiously optimistic about the stock’s prospects.
